# ─── Cloud Sync (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Cloud Sync lets you push an M3U/Xtream URL from a phone or browser to the TV
# instead of typing long URLs with the remote. It is COMPLETELY OPTIONAL —
# M3U URL and Xtream Codes direct-entry work without any of this.
#
# To enable, create a free Supabase project at https://supabase.com,
# run docs/cloud-sync/schema.sql in the SQL editor, then fill in:
#
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
#
# The anon key is safe to embed in a client-side app (Supabase design);
# Row Level Security on the database enforces that each TV can only access
# its own data, and only when the correct device key is presented.
#
# Alternative: skip this file and configure at runtime via
# Settings → Cloud Sync Yapılandırması on the TV.
